1
00:00:25,640 --> 00:00:26,320
Su Zhuang.

2
00:00:26,600 --> 00:00:27,519
Go call the police, quick.

3
00:00:27,519 --> 00:00:29,000
Godfather, don't call the police. It's me.

4
00:00:29,640 --> 00:00:31,359
Godfather, do you want to go to prison?

5
00:00:31,359 --> 00:00:32,320
He's a cop.

6
00:01:26,159 --> 00:01:27,239
The reason I'm telling you all this

7
00:01:28,680 --> 00:01:29,719
is because I want you to know

8
00:01:30,879 --> 00:01:32,480
men with twisted minds

9
00:01:32,879 --> 00:01:34,000
are often especially skilled at hiding

10
00:01:34,000 --> 00:01:35,480
their true thoughts and actions.

11
00:01:37,040 --> 00:01:38,400
On the surface, they might seem

12
00:01:38,400 --> 00:01:39,680
no different from normal people.

13
00:01:40,359 --> 00:01:41,760
Even more normal than normal people.

14
00:01:42,120 --> 00:01:43,480
They deliberately craft

15
00:01:44,000 --> 00:01:46,079
a perfect, harmless image of themselves.

16
00:01:46,719 --> 00:01:47,319
Bro Li.

17
00:01:49,319 --> 00:01:50,159
I'm scared.

18
00:01:50,439 --> 00:01:51,400
What are you afraid of?

19
00:01:52,120 --> 00:01:53,000
We're here for you.

20
00:01:53,799 --> 00:01:55,159
Our whole team is your family.

21
00:01:56,280 --> 00:01:56,840
Right?

22
00:02:02,239 --> 00:02:04,640
Like the last glove at the sanatorium,

23
00:02:04,920 --> 00:02:05,799
no trace at all.

24
00:02:06,760 --> 00:02:08,520
Skin cells, hair, sweat,

25
00:02:08,639 --> 00:02:09,560
nothing was found.

26
00:02:26,360 --> 00:02:26,800
Hello?

27
00:02:27,240 --> 00:02:27,919
Captain Li.

28
00:02:28,439 --> 00:02:29,120
Su Zhuang's awake.

29
00:02:32,199 --> 00:02:33,599
Start the interrogation right away.

30
00:02:35,560 --> 00:02:36,159
What's wrong?

31
00:02:36,319 --> 00:02:37,319
Captain Wang's already in there.

32
00:02:40,479 --> 00:02:41,360
What did you say to him?

33
00:02:41,960 --> 00:02:42,599
Stop right there.

34
00:02:44,639 --> 00:02:46,199
Why did you meet the suspect alone?

35
00:02:46,879 --> 00:02:48,599
Li Kaiyang, what's your problem?

36
00:02:49,319 --> 00:02:51,039
I'm now Head of the Special Task Force.

37
00:02:51,360 --> 00:02:53,280
Do I have to report my words to you?

38
00:02:53,800 --> 00:02:55,639
By protocol, shouldn't you have informed me?

39
00:02:56,039 --> 00:02:57,080
When you meet a suspect,

40
00:02:57,199 --> 00:02:58,199
shouldn't I be present?

41
00:02:58,199 --> 00:02:59,439
I want to solve the case quickly.

42
00:02:59,879 --> 00:03:01,360
Solving cases has its own rules.

43
00:03:01,520 --> 00:03:02,360
What rules?

44
00:03:03,039 --> 00:03:05,520
Since when does Li Kaiyang set the rules?

45
00:03:05,639 --> 00:03:07,159
Are rules set by a single person?

46
00:03:07,800 --> 00:03:09,280
Rules are set by the law.

47
00:03:11,039 --> 00:03:12,319
You've only been back a few days.

48
00:03:13,039 --> 00:03:14,400
How much do you know about this case?

49
00:03:15,560 --> 00:03:16,159
Do you have any idea

50
00:03:16,159 --> 00:03:18,240
how much effort we've put into this case?

51
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:21,199
We were just about to see a breakthrough.

52
00:03:21,520 --> 00:03:22,800
And you barge right in.

53
00:03:23,199 --> 00:03:24,560
Don't you know it'll throw off our rhythm?

54
00:03:25,400 --> 00:03:27,319
All our work will go to waste, got it?

55
00:03:27,719 --> 00:03:29,080
What do you mean "barge in"?

56
00:03:29,879 --> 00:03:31,080
As Head of the Special Task Force,

57
00:03:31,080 --> 00:03:32,680
do I have no right to question this case?

58
00:03:35,280 --> 00:03:36,680
Big deal, Head of the Special Task Force!

59
00:03:37,680 --> 00:03:39,039
Do you solve cases with authority?

60
00:03:40,159 --> 00:03:42,039
It takes everyone's combined effort.

61
00:03:42,919 --> 00:03:44,240
Only by uniting everyone's strength

62
00:03:44,319 --> 00:03:45,360
can we break through the fog

63
00:03:45,360 --> 00:03:46,360
and uncover the truth.

64
00:03:46,919 --> 00:03:48,919
How can anyone work with you like this?

65
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:53,199
It's fine if you don't respect me.

66
00:03:53,560 --> 00:03:54,599
I can't be bothered to argue with you.

67
00:03:54,599 --> 00:03:55,439
You outrank me.

68
00:03:56,080 --> 00:03:57,560
Fine, I'm telling you now.

69
00:03:58,120 --> 00:03:59,599
Su Zhuang won't say a word at all.

70
00:04:00,400 --> 00:04:01,639
If you're so capable, pry his mouth open.

71
00:04:17,000 --> 00:04:18,519
They say when a person falls ill,

72
00:04:19,720 --> 00:04:20,759
their heart softens.

73
00:04:21,480 --> 00:04:22,879
How come yours has only hardened?

74
00:04:29,000 --> 00:04:30,199
What on earth is the reason

75
00:04:31,439 --> 00:04:32,920
that made you go completely silent?

76
00:04:41,120 --> 00:04:42,399
In all my years as a cop,

77
00:04:45,120 --> 00:04:46,160
I've seen plenty of ruthless,

78
00:04:46,879 --> 00:04:48,680
cold-blooded suspects.

79
00:04:50,560 --> 00:04:51,519
More than I can count.

80
00:04:52,120 --> 00:04:54,399
But to watch your own woman

81
00:04:55,360 --> 00:04:56,279
and your own child

82
00:04:57,399 --> 00:04:58,439
get murdered before your eyes,

83
00:04:59,639 --> 00:05:01,040
and still feel nothing,

84
00:05:06,120 --> 00:05:06,920
you're the first.

85
00:05:22,879 --> 00:05:24,600
Shen Qing's death

86
00:05:38,519 --> 00:05:39,680
was a suicide.

87
00:05:54,079 --> 00:05:55,560
Did you ever think about having a child?

88
00:05:58,399 --> 00:05:59,439
You must have.

89
00:06:02,399 --> 00:06:04,279
That's why you were with Shen Qing.

90
00:06:09,040 --> 00:06:10,399
But you surely never imagined

91
00:06:11,920 --> 00:06:12,879
that your child

92
00:06:13,800 --> 00:06:15,480
would never even see this world,

93
00:06:18,800 --> 00:06:21,279
or even develop into a child,

94
00:06:23,600 --> 00:06:24,800
and would leave it behind

95
00:06:26,519 --> 00:06:27,720
in such a way.

96
00:06:32,759 --> 00:06:35,079
Did you see Shen Qing's gift for the baby?

97
00:06:41,040 --> 00:06:41,720
Right.

98
00:06:44,399 --> 00:06:45,959
If you'd seen it sooner,

99
00:06:49,600 --> 00:06:50,680
maybe she wouldn't have had to die.

100
00:06:52,040 --> 00:06:52,959
What gift?

101
00:07:02,000 --> 00:07:02,800
You want to know?

102
00:07:05,279 --> 00:07:06,360
If you want to know,

103
00:07:08,319 --> 00:07:09,519
I can take you to see it.

104
00:07:11,160 --> 00:07:11,720
Boss.

105
00:07:12,519 --> 00:07:13,399
Chief Xing gave orders

106
00:07:13,839 --> 00:07:15,720
the suspect cannot leave until recovered.

107
00:07:15,959 --> 00:07:16,839
He's worried something might go wrong.

108
00:07:17,759 --> 00:07:18,720
I've reported to Chief Xing.

109
00:07:19,319 --> 00:07:20,399
He approved my action.

110
00:07:24,160 --> 00:07:24,720
All right.

111
00:08:23,879 --> 00:08:25,000
I can give you some time

112
00:08:27,720 --> 00:08:28,560
so you can

113
00:08:30,040 --> 00:08:30,839
take a good look yourself.

114
00:09:39,720 --> 00:09:40,720
Be good, baby

115
00:09:41,159 --> 00:09:42,080
Say "Daddy"

116
00:09:43,320 --> 00:09:44,440
Daddy

117
00:09:58,759 --> 00:09:59,559
Son

118
00:10:06,559 --> 00:10:07,120
Good boy

119
00:10:25,919 --> 00:10:26,879
I'm sorry

120
00:10:29,080 --> 00:10:29,960
I'm sorry

121
00:10:43,759 --> 00:10:44,480
Shen Qing

122
00:10:45,120 --> 00:10:45,840
Shen Qing

123
00:10:46,960 --> 00:10:47,679
My son

124
00:10:48,480 --> 00:10:49,279
My son

125
00:10:50,320 --> 00:10:51,279
Shen Qing

126
00:10:52,200 --> 00:10:53,559
I know I was wrong

127
00:10:53,559 --> 00:10:55,440
I know I was wrong

128
00:10:56,320 --> 00:10:57,720
I've failed you both

129
00:10:59,679 --> 00:11:01,559
Please don't leave me

130
00:11:01,559 --> 00:11:03,279
Don't leave me

131
00:11:07,080 --> 00:11:09,000
I'm the one who hurt you

132
00:11:15,039 --> 00:11:17,159
I'm the one who hurt you

133
00:11:23,679 --> 00:11:25,360
I'm a sinner

134
00:11:28,399 --> 00:11:30,320
This is all my retribution

135
00:11:30,960 --> 00:11:32,840
My retribution

136
00:11:47,960 --> 00:11:50,240
I deserve worse than death.

137
00:11:53,720 --> 00:11:55,799
I deserve it.

138
00:11:58,919 --> 00:12:00,080
I deserve to die.

139
00:12:00,840 --> 00:12:01,960
I deserve to die.

140
00:12:02,360 --> 00:12:03,759
I deserve to die.

141
00:12:09,720 --> 00:12:10,879
Even if you kill yourself,

142
00:12:13,200 --> 00:12:13,919
what good would it do?

143
00:12:14,200 --> 00:12:15,159
What could you possibly undo?

144
00:12:16,519 --> 00:12:19,159
I'm begging you, just kill me.

145
00:12:19,840 --> 00:12:21,399
If you want to redeem yourself,

146
00:12:24,000 --> 00:12:24,840
tell the truth.

147
00:12:28,279 --> 00:12:30,159
Whatever you want to know,

148
00:12:31,399 --> 00:12:33,039
I'll tell you everything.

149
00:12:52,360 --> 00:12:53,039
Su Zhuang.

150
00:12:53,360 --> 00:12:54,279
Go call the police, now!

151
00:12:54,279 --> 00:12:55,759
Godfather, don't call. It's me.

152
00:12:56,360 --> 00:12:58,080
Godfather, do you want to go to jail?

153
00:12:58,080 --> 00:12:59,039
He's a cop.

154
00:13:10,399 --> 00:13:11,080
Godfather.

155
00:13:12,240 --> 00:13:13,159
It's because of him

156
00:13:14,080 --> 00:13:15,080
investigating Shen Qing's case

157
00:13:15,200 --> 00:13:16,159
that Shen Qing ended up dead.

158
00:13:17,240 --> 00:13:18,320
And your son, too.

159
00:13:23,399 --> 00:13:24,799
Don't add crime to crime.

160
00:13:35,200 --> 00:13:35,720
Godfather.

161
00:13:36,440 --> 00:13:37,039
Godfather!

162
00:13:37,399 --> 00:13:37,960
Captain Li!

163
00:13:38,120 --> 00:13:38,639
Let's go, quick!

164
00:13:38,840 --> 00:13:39,600
Captain Li!

165
00:13:40,720 --> 00:13:41,399
Captain Li!

166
00:13:45,039 --> 00:13:46,000
Over here, over here!

167
00:13:47,559 --> 00:13:49,240
A Tai, the cops will be here any minute.

168
00:13:49,240 --> 00:13:50,360
Where can we possibly run to?

169
00:13:50,360 --> 00:13:51,679
Don't worry. I've got it all arranged.

170
00:13:51,840 --> 00:13:52,559
Godfather, slow down.

171
00:15:46,919 --> 00:15:47,519
A Tai

172
00:15:47,840 --> 00:15:48,679
Why did you stop the car?

173
00:15:48,840 --> 00:15:49,480
Godfather

174
00:15:50,120 --> 00:15:51,039
You drive from here

175
00:15:51,480 --> 00:15:52,600
I'll lead the cops away

176
00:15:52,879 --> 00:15:54,879
No, I can't just leave you behind

177
00:15:55,320 --> 00:15:55,960
Besides

178
00:15:56,519 --> 00:15:57,519
With that many cops

179
00:15:57,720 --> 00:15:58,679
I can't escape anyway

180
00:15:59,200 --> 00:15:59,759
Godfather

181
00:16:00,360 --> 00:16:02,000
Just keep driving down this path

182
00:16:02,000 --> 00:16:02,919
Someone's waiting up ahead

183
00:16:03,120 --> 00:16:04,000
Hurry, hurry!

184
00:16:04,000 --> 00:16:05,120
There's no time left
